We are pleased to announce the aSSB'15 Thematic Research School on "advance=
s in Systems and Synthetic Biology - Modelling complex biological systems i=
n the context of genomics". The upcoming session will take place in Strasbo=
urg on 23-27 March 2015. The program will include conferences (the speakers=
